== Memory Map ==

* 0x000000 - 0x000007 = ROM Vectors (16-bits)
* 0x000008 - 0x007FFF = 32KB Internal SRAM (16-bits)
* 0x008000 - 0x00BFFF = 16KB ROM (16-bits)
* 0x00C000 - 0x00FFFF = 16KB Internal SRAM (16-bits)
* 0x01004x = VDU base (A0 = 0) (8-bits)
* 0x01004x = ACIA base (A0 = 1) (8-bits)
* 0x200000-0x20FFFF = 64KB Internal SRAM (16-bits)
* 0x210000-0x217FFF = 32KB Internal SRAM (16-bits)
* 0x300000 - 0x3FFFFF - 1MB External SRAM (8-bits)

